{"type": "article", "id": 4328, "title": "Otura 组合柜", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-12T07:50:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233337XdhvEZt1uSONKmL7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在今年的伊斯坦布尔设计双年展上，来自荷兰的设计师 Rianne Koens 推出了一款模块化的木柜组合，整个组合柜由 6 个大小不同的抽屉与柜子组合而成，既可以整套使用或将其中几个单品组合使用，也可以分拆为单个的凳子或者小边桌。每一件单品都能独立自由移动，摆放在任意你觉得合适的位置，作为凳子和边桌使用时，你只需将隐藏在底部的支架撑开即可。定价 145－295 欧元不等，<a href=\"http://www.oturadesign.com/otura-basic/#order\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233335JOauP2Tkf1U9DlZM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6640625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233335r1u6AqBWYhHKDZEy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233336Jv5wpEoUZN0TrRAB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233336ObcIZfU9RFjW1Gdw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.7140625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}